<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ema612_05_IH_0001</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema612_05.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema612_05_ih_0001 paging">
      <section class="title type2 score">
        <h2 data-head="1_green" lang="y">각기둥의 전개도를 보고 물음에 답해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <div class="question_box align_start">
            <div class="img_area mr_20">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA612_05_IH/0001_01.png" alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="input_area">
              <h3 lang="y">밑면과 옆면의 모양을 각각 써 보세요.</h3>
              <div class="input_row">
                <span lang="y">밑면의 모양:</span>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="육각형(또는 정육각형)" data-answer-multi='{"values": ["육각형", "정육각형"]}' text-align="center" class="large"></math-field>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="input_row">
                <span lang="y">옆면의 모양:</span>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="직사각형" text-align="center" class="large"></math-field>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">밑면의 모양은 육각형, 옆면의 모양은 직사각형 입니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <div class="question_box align_start">
            <div class="img_area mr_20">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA612_05_IH/0001_01.png" alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="input_area">
              <h3 lang="y">전개도를 접었을 때 만들어지는 각기둥의 이름을 고르세요.</h3>
              <div class="dropdown_wrap">
                <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="육각기둥">
                  <option></option>
                  <option value="삼각기둥"></option>
                  <option value="사각기둥"></option>
                  <option value="오각기둥"></option>
                  <option value="육각기둥"></option>
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">밑면의 모양이 육각형이므로 전개도를 접었을 때 만들어지는 각기둥은 육각기둥입니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
